name: We're all made of time
description:
a little boy from a dream asked me which one was created first? man or time? I was silent by the question, I can't answer it right now but I believe we are created by time. Time just is like air, we breathe the same air and we age at the same moment.

on our way, we will learn many things, meet new people, but if you are lucky you will meet your soul mate and share the same space & time.

Time is a very precious gift from God to us. With that, I will pass the precious little time I have for my children & family.

Submission for #AMJO2 #NFTPrizedMoments.
Pixelart 200x250px resize to 1000x1500 px
Frame by Frame animation (215 frames in total)
